data.description:
Discover your dream home on this sprawling 6-acre estate, perfect for country living with modern luxuries. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home combines charm and functionality, offering a sanctuary for both you and your animals. Horse lovers will appreciate the expansive pasture land, while the multiple barns provide endless possibilities for livestock or storage.

The main attraction is the stunning 60ft x 40ft red barn, boasting a versatile room that can be transformed into a man cave, she shed, or game room. Additional outbuildings and shops cater to all your agricultural or hobbyist needs.

Inside the residence, you're welcomed by a cozy atmosphere with modern amenities. The open-concept kitchen flows into the living area, ideal for hosting. Step outside and you're greeted by an in-ground pool, the perfect spot for cooling off on hot summer days or entertaining friends and family.

This property isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle. Make it yours today!
